            May 2021
            We’re excited to announce the second iteration of the Independent Summer Statistics Community: Beyond Coursework. Through this community, Department of Statistical Sciences students will have opportunities to build their professional statistical portfolio, connect with other students, increase their career preparedness and explore their options.
            Who is it for? All undergraduate students in a Department of Statistical Sciences (UTSG) PoST (including those about to graduate) or who took STA130 in Fall 2020/Winter 2021.
